snippet.title: Kota`s New Journey - Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam! store.steampowered.com/app/3270680/Kotas_New_Journey/

This is a cute, funny and slightly cheesy sfw game about the adventures of an elf cosplayer, absolutely nothing to do with popular manga and anime. Also, this game is totally free. It has no in-game purchases, ads, paywalls and other bullshit. No, it's a completely free, albeit small, game whose main goal is to make the player smile.
